{"tid":1126513,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩連奴暗示：曼聯球員叫我習大大","createTime":"2019-04-26T12:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T15:00:26.000Z","uid":17641,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"78f4dd11739e098bddf44cfc507d31e0e9f99865","tid":1126513,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T12:16:57.000Z","msg":"曼聯近期表現不知所謂，難聽啲講仲衰過摩連奴執教嗰時，因此就有傳媒諗起摩連奴，旁敲則擊想佢爆更多當日執教曼聯時嘅情況，摩連奴跑慣江湖當然唔會指名道姓，但佢就暗示，有球員叫佢做雜種，仲鬧呢啲球員根本冇野心爭冠軍，係冇用嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n摩連奴話：「我會為球隊帶來能力、知識、經驗及無盡嘅野心，但當我失敗時我係一個好差嘅人，對於嗰啲冇野心嘅人，我都係一個好差嘅人。」<br />\n<br />\n佢仲話：「球員點樣形容我？有啲球員叫我混蛋、雜種，佢哋都係啲冇野心，唔敢爭冠軍嘅人。」"},{"pid":"ad676991fcd9ce3669135a10bcf4ed39a1748c10","tid":1126513,"uid":115150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T12:17:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c4d48c56bba5a86aec63a2f6faf7744475a871","tid":1126513,"uid":60432,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T12:18:06.000Z","msg":"佢連榜尾都唔攻搶分仲話爭冠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95fb0da5e2738bee4200f5958f329d95fd40f5d5","tid":1126513,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T12:25:03.000Z","msg":"睇到後面笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e79488c3916eefcdc0521bf96305668a67f855","tid":1126513,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T12:29:15.000Z","msg":"haha"},{"pid":"10c6cdbde1fe9df5b904ca6d166da26b4be8d112","tid":1126513,"uid":96964,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T12:32:58.000Z","msg":"中文幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b118d7d5f43605e95ea3b334a6e05c51c2f035d8","tid":1126513,"uid":37528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T12:34:19.000Z","msg":"我會為球隊帶來能力、知識、經驗及無盡嘅野心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/